{"tid":2405413,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)新年節目-五福星系列","createTime":"2021-02-12T10:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T17:03:05.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6f33c478caeef433b306ce1c5ff7b71641af6fad","tid":2405413,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">支肺已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=416513f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=d75a5e69\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=ba6145f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n奇謀妙計五福星:茶壺、死氣喉、凡士林、鬈毛積及劉克司五人出獄後決改邪歸正，與鬈毛積之妹(妹頭)同組「五寶清潔公司」。某次匪徒正交易偽鈔電版時遇劫匪，剛巧被 CID 看見便一路追趕，後劫匪情急下將電版拋進五福星之清潔車中。 五寶開始被兩大反派追殺，最後五福星施展奇謀妙計應付兩大反派。<br />\n<br />\n福星高照:一個腐敗的香港警察三哥（林正英）攜帶大批鑽石財寶去了日本投靠了黑幫「稻草人俱樂部」。瑞奇和大力丸（成龍）奉命追至日本緝拿，他們在地鐵發現了三哥，並且去追，追到遊樂場，三哥的接應人日本黑幫前來阻擋，三哥被走脫了，而瑞奇被黑幫一棍子打昏，抓了起來。雞骨草打了個電話，叫曹警司（曹達華）叫鷓鴣菜前來日本幫忙<br />\n<br />\n夏日福星:鷓鴣菜(洪金寶飾)、羅漢果(曾志偉飾)、花旗蔘(秦祥林飾)、大生地(吳耀漢飾)及犀牛皮(馮淬帆飾)在東京屢破奇案，香港警察特地請他們到泰國芭提雅渡假，而花旗蔘(秦祥林飾)因準備行船，故推薦其弟花塔餅(苗僑偉飾)代替自己加入五福星行列。霸王花(胡慧中飾)同時亦接獲密令，往泰國找線人老馬(黃錦燊飾)，拿一份泰、港毒販名單，但殺手已搶先將其滅口，幸馬於臨終前已將名單寄往香港的王綺清小姐(關芝琳飾)，於是五福星聯同香港警探雞骨草(成龍飾)與獨腳金(元彪飾)會師再戰.....<br />\n<br />\n五福星撞鬼:外號叫&ldquo;鷓鴣菜&rdquo;&ldquo;羅漢果&rdquo;&ldquo;犀牛皮&rdquo;&ldquo;花旗參&rdquo;和&ldquo;大山地&rdquo;的五個香港青年整日想入非非，即想輕鬆賺錢，又想有漂亮的女友相伴，但又不想塌實乾事，結果一事無成，只能得過且過，混日子，打發時光。一次，他們五人一同去旅遊勝地&mdash;&mdash;離島遊玩，卻不料晚上在島上的一棟黑漆漆的大屋內撞到一男一女兩個鬼魂。第二天，他們向有關警局報了警.....<br />\n<br />\n運財五福星:賭王雷天，在一次頂級國際頂級睹術大賽中被賭花上宮飛花陷害而落敗，身敗名裂以至吞槍自殺。其女慧琳誓要為父報仇並求助雷天生前好友華叔，華叔於是重召五福星幫忙&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n6 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完左再算可能魔戒1-6或滴滴尼MARVEL<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=a4b45efc\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=128d2441\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3568def6b47c7d879963d47e012100d79d23de","tid":2405413,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7d/Lucky_Stars.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu